item.description:
Selected 2nd years for Programming Society

Selecting a few out of many was a humungous task for us. Still we tried our best to be impartial in our decisions and every selection was democratically done taking into consideration the summary mailed by the fellow students and the participation he/she had shown during 1st year of his/her studies.
